```json
{
"application": "MLPerf",
"other_software": [
"MLPerf Logging",
"NCCL",
"IBV",
"Nvidia-smi",
"SSH",
"Slurm",
"Jet",
"CUDNN",
"PyTorch",
"MaskRCNN"
],
"resource_requirements": {
"DGXSYSTEM": "Required, not set by default",
"CONT": "Required, not set by default",
"MLPERF_RULESET": "Optional, defaults to 3.1.0",
"MLPERF_CLUSTER_NAME": "Optional, defaults to 'unknown'",
"NEXP": "Optional, defaults to 1",
"DATESTAMP": "Optional, defaults to current date and time",
"CLEAR_CACHES": "Optional, defaults to 1",
"CHECK_COMPLIANCE": "Optional, defaults to 1",
"LOGDIR": "Optional, defaults to ./results",
"API_LOG_DIR": "Optional, defaults to ./api_logs",
"ABSLOGDIR": "Optional, defaults to ${PWD}/results",
"POWERCMDDIR": "Optional, defaults to ' '",
"TIME_TAGS": "Optional, defaults to 0",
"NVTX_FLAG": "Optional, defaults to 0",
"NCCL_TEST": "Optional, defaults to 1",
"SYNTH_DATA": "Optional, defaults to 0",
"EPOCH_PROF": "Optional, defaults to 0",
"DISABLE_CG": "Optional, defaults to 0",
"COCO2017PYT_DIR": "Required, must be set to the directory containing the COCO2017 PYT dataset",
"NVMLPERF_NSIGHT_LOCATION": "Required if NVTX_FLAG is set to 1",
"JET_DIR": "Required if JET is set to 1",
"DATADIR": "Required, must be set to the directory containing the data",
"PKLPATH": "Required, must be set to the directory containing the PKL files",
"JET_CREATE": "Optional, used to create a Jet file",
"JET_UPLOAD": "Optional, used to upload a Jet file"
}
}
```
